<p align="justify">The 7th Festival of Inventors, initiatives, and Innovation 2019 recognized the Intelligent Family Pharmacy (Mobile App) as the National Innovator Award winner. This app is a smart solution for managing family health, and medication needs and alleviating drug consumption issues.
The project is headed by <a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=sT0YnDIAAAAJ&hl=en&oi=sra">Dr. Mohammad-Hossein Nadimi-Shahraki</a> as the principal investigator and Hoda Zamani as the co-principal investigator.
